metadata.name: Rio De Janeiro - 1979
metadata.description:
Shot on Super 8 Film
Camera and the expired film were in storage for the last 40 years. This film include unedited, raw footage featuring model Juliana Nalu in Brazil, January 2022.

A limited edition 1 of 1 work,, Includes no audio so the owner can eventually display it on a screen playing to whichever song they feel in the moment. Play in loop
